ode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aSemiotics and literature. 4aLiteratur. 4aLiteraturwissenschaften. 4aSprachwissenschaften. 4aTheater. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aHenschelmann, Käthe.1 aNelting, David, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Literary and Cultural Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110637854oZDB-23-GLC0 cprintz978348422064540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311094672740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110946727423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110946727/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GLCc2000d2014